{"type": "article", "id": 25901, "title": "这 16 样东西，好像从来都没有真的有用", "description": "一开始没有意识到……", "date": "2016-04-24T07:39:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 380, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130308dmxsNFHtYSbGBXEl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <br></p>\n<p><b>1. 新年计划。健身计划。早睡计划。情绪管理计划。刚恋爱时的人生计划。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130259JnGlF8T7IPChyq30.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 伞套。@ 何东宜    <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130259BzLFJdVmpW8COQHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 放假带回家看的书。@</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130259OHdz76f9va1T4W5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 收藏的各类学习类视频、长文章。<br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021303009C4aAqQRpiZwFyMx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 背单词/健身/记账 app。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130300lq34v1tHMQzIPEnK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.464\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>6. 下载完其他浏览器之后的 ie 浏览器。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130301EdHLCqFi6KPZUIMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>7. 阅读并接受以上条款...  @ sjycjot</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-inser